data.description: The specious layout of this home is perfect for a growing family. This house features  5 Bedrooms, 3 Full Bathrooms with (1 bedroom and full bath downstairs) and 2679 SQFT. The house has new carpet throughout the home provides a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is a chef's dream with a large island counter bar with sink and all new stainless steel appliances , dishwasher, microwave with a hood fan and gas stove oven. The one bedroom and full bath downstairs offers convenience and flexibility for guests or multigeneration living arrangements. The large backyard is blank canvas waiting for your personal touch. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a beautiful and specious home in a well-maintained neighborhood.
